{"tha-ap415:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap415:0.2":"Bhaddalivagga ","tha-ap415:0.3":"3 Tinasulakachadaniyattheraapadana ","tha-ap415:1.1":"“Jatim jaranca maranam, ","tha-ap415:1.2":"paccavekkhim aham tada; ","tha-ap415:1.3":"Ekako abhinikkhamma, ","tha-ap415:1.4":"pabbajim anagariyam. ","tha-ap415:2.1":"Caramanonupubbena, ","tha-ap415:2.2":"gangatiram upagamim; ","tha-ap415:2.3":"Tatthaddasasim pathavim, ","tha-ap415:2.4":"gangatire samunnatam. ","tha-ap415:3.1":"Assamam tattha mapetva, ","tha-ap415:3.2":"vasami assame aham; ","tha-ap415:3.3":"Sukato cankamo mayham, ","tha-ap415:3.4":"nanadijaganayuto. ","tha-ap415:4.1":"Mamupenti ca vissattha, ","tha-ap415:4.2":"kujanti ca manoharam; ","tha-ap415:4.3":"Ramamano saha tehi, ","tha-ap415:4.4":"vasami assame aham. ","tha-ap415:5.1":"Mama assamasamanta, ","tha-ap415:5.2":"migaraja catukkamo; ","tha-ap415:5.3":"Asaya abhinikkhamma, ","tha-ap415:5.4":"gajji so asani viya. ","tha-ap415:6.1":"Nadite migaraje ca, ","tha-ap415:6.2":"haso me udapajjatha; ","tha-ap415:6.3":"Migarajam gavesanto, ","tha-ap415:6.4":"addasam lokanayakam. ","tha-ap415:7.1":"Disvanaham devadevam, ","tha-ap415:7.2":"tissam lokagganayakam; ","tha-ap415:7.3":"Hattho hatthena cittena, ","tha-ap415:7.4":"pujayim nagakesaram. ","tha-ap415:8.1":"Uggacchantamva suriyam, ","tha-ap415:8.2":"salarajamva pupphitam; ","tha-ap415:8.3":"Osadhimva virocantam, ","tha-ap415:8.4":"santhavim lokanayakam. ","tha-ap415:9.1":"‘Tava nanena sabbannu, ","tha-ap415:9.2":"mocesimam sadevakam; ","tha-ap415:9.3":"Tavam aradhayitvana, ","tha-ap415:9.4":"jatiya parimuccare. ","tha-ap415:10.1":"Adassanena sabbannu, ","tha-ap415:10.2":"buddhanam sabbadassinam; ","tha-ap415:10.3":"Patantivicinirayam, ","tha-ap415:10.4":"ragadosehi ophuta. ","tha-ap415:11.1":"Tava dassanamagamma, ","tha-ap415:11.2":"sabbannu lokanayaka; ","tha-ap415:11.3":"Pamuccanti bhava sabba, ","tha-ap415:11.4":"phusanti amatam padam. ","tha-ap415:12.1":"Yada buddha cakkhumanto, ","tha-ap415:12.2":"uppajjanti pabhankara; ","tha-ap415:12.3":"Kilese jhapayitvana, ","tha-ap415:12.4":"alokam dassayanti te’. ","tha-ap415:13.1":"Kittayitvana sambuddham, ","tha-ap415:13.2":"tissam lokagganayakam; ","tha-ap415:13.3":"Hattho hatthena cittena, ","tha-ap415:13.4":"tinasulam apujayim. ","tha-ap415:14.1":"Mama sankappamannaya, ","tha-ap415:14.2":"tisso lokagganayako; ","tha-ap415:14.3":"Sakasane nisiditva, ","tha-ap415:14.4":"ima gatha abhasatha. ","tha-ap415:15.1":"‘Yo mam pupphehi chadesi, ","tha-ap415:15.2":"pasanno sehi panibhi; ","tha-ap415:15.3":"Tamaham kittayissami, ","tha-ap415:15.4":"sunatha mama bhasato. ","tha-ap415:16.1":"Pancavisatikkhattum so, ","tha-ap415:16.2":"devarajjam karissati; ","tha-ap415:16.3":"Pancasattatikkhattunca, ","tha-ap415:16.4":"cakkavatti bhavissati. ","tha-ap415:17.1":"Padesarajjam vipulam, ","tha-ap415:17.2":"gananato asankhiyam; ","tha-ap415:17.3":"Tassa kammanissandena, ","tha-ap415:17.4":"pupphanam pujanaya ca. ","tha-ap415:18.1":"Sisamnhato cayam poso, ","tha-ap415:18.2":"pupphamakankhate yadi; ","tha-ap415:18.3":"Punnakammena samyuttam, ","tha-ap415:18.4":"purato patubhavissati. ","tha-ap415:19.1":"Yam yam icchati kamehi, ","tha-ap415:19.2":"tam tam patubhavissati; ","tha-ap415:19.3":"Sankappam paripuretva, ","tha-ap415:19.4":"nibbayissatinasavo’. ","tha-ap415:20.1":"Attharasamam bhanavaram. ","tha-ap415:21.1":"Kilese jhapayitvana, ","tha-ap415:21.2":"sampajano patissato; ","tha-ap415:21.3":"Ekasane nisiditva, ","tha-ap415:21.4":"arahattamapapunim. ","tha-ap415:22.1":"Cankamanto nipajjanto, ","tha-ap415:22.2":"nisinno uda va thito; ","tha-ap415:22.3":"Buddhasettham saritvana, ","tha-ap415:22.4":"viharami aham sada. ","tha-ap415:23.1":"Civare pindapate ca, ","tha-ap415:23.2":"paccaye sayanasane; ","tha-ap415:23.3":"Tattha me unata natthi, ","tha-ap415:23.4":"buddhapujayidam phalam. ","tha-ap415:24.1":"So dani patto amatam, ","tha-ap415:24.2":"santam padamanuttaram; ","tha-ap415:24.3":"Sabbasave parinnaya, ","tha-ap415:24.4":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap415:25.1":"Dvenavute ito kappe, ","tha-ap415:25.2":"yam pupphamabhipujayim; ","tha-ap415:25.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap415:25.4":"buddhapujayidam phalam. ","tha-ap415:26.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","tha-ap415:26.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap415:26.3":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap415:27.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","tha-ap415:27.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap415:27.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","tha-ap415:28.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap415:28.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap415:28.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap415:29.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma tinasulakachadaniyo thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap415:30.1":"Tinasulakachadaniyattherassapadanam tatiyam. "}